Package: Climatastic
Type: Package
Title: US Climate Reference Network package for R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: c(person("Andrew", "Halajian", email = "ah697@cornell.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Caroline", "Sun", email = "cs979@cornell.edu", role = c("aut", "cre") ) )
Description: Functions to conduct statistical analyses of the daily data from weather stations maintained by the National Centers for ENvironmental Information (NCEI), 
\url{https: //www.ncei.noaa.gov/pub/data/uscrn/products/daily01/}. Retreive yearly trends and averages of temperature over time.
